name: Rocky Point Ice Cream
address: 2800 Murray St, Port Moody, BC V3H 1X2, Canada

hasMenuItem.name: Double Chocolate Raspberry
hasMenuItem.description:
Our house-made chocolate ice cream base from scratch using 100% cocoa mass, adding in generous amounts of dark chocolate flake inclusions and house-made raspberry coulis, rippled throughout. 
Contains Soy, Eggs, Dairy, Vodka (in the raspberry coulis).

hasMenuItem.name: Rocky Point Road
hasMenuItem.description:
Our house-made chocolate ice cream base is made from scratch in-house using 100% pure cocoa mass. Adding in fluffy marshmallows and tamari almond inclusions throughout. 
Contains Gluten, Soy, Almonds, Eggs, Gelatin, Dairy.

hasMenuItem.name: Cookie Dough
hasMenuItem.description:
Our house-made vanilla ice cream base with generous amounts of dark chocolate flakes and cookie dough pieces throughout. 
Contains Gluten, Soy, Eggs, Dairy.

hasMenuItem.name: Salted Caramel
hasMenuItem.description:
Our most popular flavour! Hand-made caramel from scratch is infused in our house-made ice cream base with our secret blend of sea salt. Because this sweet and savoury treat is hand-made with love, every batch may taste a little different due to the darkness of the caramel.
Contains Eggs, Dairy.

hasMenuItem.name: Cookies N Cream
hasMenuItem.description:
Our house-made vanilla ice cream base with generous amounts of crushed Oreo cookies throughout.
Contains Gluten, Soy, Eggs, Dairy.

hasMenuItem.name: Earl Grey & Honey
hasMenuItem.description:
Our house-made ice cream base is cold steeped overnight with earl grey tea from Unmediocre Kitchen in Port Moody and real honey.  
Contains Eggs, Dairy.

hasMenuItem.name: Banana Fudge
hasMenuItem.description:
Whole pureed bananas in our house-made ice cream base with house-made chocolate fudge rippled throughout.
Contains Eggs, Dairy.

hasMenuItem.name: Cookie Jar
hasMenuItem.description:
Layers of Cookies n Cream, Chocolate, and Cookie Dough Ice Cream resting on a bed of Oreo cookie crumbs and crunchy chocolate fudge. Topped with cookie dough bits, oreos and fudge
*Please note 4" does not contain a chocolate layer due to size

hasMenuItem.name: Brown Butter Pecan
hasMenuItem.description:
House-made brown sugar ice cream base with house-made candied pecans sprinkled throughout. 
Contains Pecans, Eggs, Dairy.

hasMenuItem.name: Chocolate Peanut Butter

hasMenuItem.description:
Our house-made ice cream base is cold steeped overnight with freshly ground Milano roasted coffee beans. We then add in a generous amount of dark chocolate flakes throughout to finish it off. 
Contains Soy, Eggs, Dairy.

hasMenuItem.name: Almond Coffee Toffee - Seasonal
hasMenuItem.description: Almond Coffee Toffee is a bold blend of flavours that’s sure to wake up your senses! With a smooth espresso ice cream base, this treat is packed with crunchy Skor pieces, roasted almonds, and a rich, house-made fudge ripple. Every bite delivers the perfect mix of creamy, nutty, and chocolatey goodness, making it an irresistible pick-me-up!

hasMenuItem.name: Salted Caramel
hasMenuItem.description:
Our most popular flavour! Hand-made caramel from scratch is infused in our house-made ice cream base with our secret blend of sea salt. Because this sweet and savoury treat is hand-made with love, every batch may taste a little different due to the darkness of the caramel.
Contains Eggs, Dairy.

hasMenuItem.name: Mint Flake
hasMenuItem.description:
Our house-made ice cream base is first infused with mint extract and finished with a generous amount of dark chocolate flakes throughout. 
Contains Soy, Eggs, Dairy.

hasMenuItem.name: Plant-Based Strawberry
hasMenuItem.description: Pureed whole strawberries infused into our house-made oat and coconut milk base.

hasMenuItem.name: Plant-Based Lemon Poppyseed
hasMenuItem.description: Juiced lemons and lemon zest are blended into our house-made oat and coconut milk base finished with poppy seeds throughout.

hasMenuItem.name: Sweet Tea & Peach Jam - Seasonal
hasMenuItem.description: Our creamy house-made ice cream base is infused with the bold, floral notes of Earl Grey tea from Unmediocre Kitchen in Port Moody, cold steeped overnight. A swirl of house-made peach jam ripple adds a fruity sweetness to this refreshingly smooth flavour.

hasMenuItem.name: Bubble Gum
hasMenuItem.description:
Every kid’s favourite! Blue bubble gum infused ice cream base with real pieces of bubble gum sprinkled throughout. 
Contains soy, eggs, dairy

hasMenuItem.name: Matcha
hasMenuItem.description: Ice cream base infused with matcha from tea & paper nook in port moody. Contains eggs. We make all our ice cream from scratch in one production facility so all our products may contain dairy, eggs, nuts, soy, and gluten.

hasMenuItem.name: Chocolate
hasMenuItem.description:
House-made chocolate ice cream base is made from scratch using 100% cocoa mass- only the finest chocolate.
Contains Dairy, Eggs

hasMenuItem.name: Plant-Based Chocolate
hasMenuItem.description: Rich and creamy plant-based chocolate milk ice cream, crafted with non-dairy ingredients for a delightful dessert experience.

hasMenuItem.name: Peanut Butter Caramel Nut - Seasonal
hasMenuItem.description: Experience the richness of our house-made peanut butter ice cream base, enhanced with creamy house-made fudge and caramel sauce swirled in during extraction. Finished with crunchy crushed peanuts, this flavour is a decadent delight!

hasMenuItem.name: Strawberry Lemonade Sorbet
hasMenuItem.description: A refreshing blend of tangy lemonade and sweet strawberries, crafted into a smooth sorbet.

hasMenuItem.name: Rum Raisin
hasMenuItem.description:
Our house-made ice cream base is infused with spiced rum, then finished with Malaga raisins and whole sultanas throughout. 
Contains Eggs, Dairy, Rum.

hasMenuItem.name: The Exorcist - Halloween Special
hasMenuItem.description: Tangy house-made lemon condensed milk ice cream base, tinted a vomitty green, & mixed with crunchy lemon biscuit pieces, it is a flavour that is both devilishly creamy and hauntingly tart.

hasMenuItem.name: Plant-Based Vampire Float - Halloween Special
hasMenuItem.description:
Sink your fangs into this hauntingly delicious plant-based delight!
Our house-made coconut vanilla ice cream takes a ghoulish turn with a mix of eerie plant-based raspberry ice cream & a wicked raspberry ripple creeping through every bite.

hasMenuItem.name: Sweet Georgia Brown - Seasonal
hasMenuItem.description: Welcome back the crowd-pleasing seasonal sensation: Sweet Georgia Brown! Indulge in the irresistible harmony of sweet and salty flavours with every spoonful.  Our famous Salted Caramel ice cream is generously swirled with ribbons of house-made fudge and variegated with crunchy house candied pecans, creating a symphony of taste and texture.  A beloved customer favourite, Sweet Georgia Brown was in such high demand that we simply had to bring it back for another round!

hasMenuItem.name: Australian Black Liquorice
hasMenuItem.description:
Real Australian soft black liquorice melted down and infused in our base with anise extract. Contains gluten, eggs. 
We make all our ice cream from scratch in one production facility so all our products may contain dairy, eggs, nuts, soy, and gluten.

hasMenuItem.name: Maple Walnut
hasMenuItem.description:
Our house-made ice cream base is infused with pure Canadian maple syrup and finished off with a generous amount of chopped walnuts throughout. 
Contains Walnuts, Eggs, Dairy.

hasMenuItem.name: Carrot Cake - Seasonal
hasMenuItem.description: Enjoy a slice of decadence with our Carrot Cake ice cream. Our house-made brown sugar ice cream base, infused with a touch of cinnamon, sets the stage for a symphony of flavors. Throughout each creamy scoop, you'll discover generous pieces of our house-made carrot cake & house-made cream cheese ripple. It's a spoonful of comfort, reminiscent of the classic dessert, crafted to perfection.

hasMenuItem.name: Peach Bellini Sorbet - Seasonal
hasMenuItem.description: This refreshing sorbet blends sweet peach schnapps with a vibrant raspberry prosecco ripple, capturing the essence of the classic cocktail in a frosty delight.

hasMenuItem.name: Birthday Cake
hasMenuItem.description:
House-made vanilla sponge cake ice cream base with rainbow sprinkles throughout. 
Contains Gluten, Soy, Eggs, Dairy.

hasMenuItem.name: K9 (for Dogs)
hasMenuItem.description:
Our plain ice cream base with dog kibble throughout and topped with a milk bone. A true treat for your four-legged best friend.
Contains Dairy, Gluten, Eggs, Sugar, Chicken, Beef.

hasMenuItem.name: Mango Sorbet
hasMenuItem.description: Smooth and creamy sorbet made from ripe mangoes, delivering a refreshing and fruity taste in every scoop.

hasMenuItem.name: Blackberry Sage - Seasonal
hasMenuItem.description: Experience the perfect balance of sweet and savory in our Blackberry Sage ice cream. Our creamy house-made base is infused with fresh blackberries and fresh aromatic sage, delivering a uniquely refreshing and indulgent treat.

hasMenuItem.name: Passionfruit Pavlova - Seasonal
hasMenuItem.description: A luscious creation featuring sweetened condensed milk ice cream infused with house-made pavlova pieces and swirls of real passionfruit coulis. This delicious blend delivers a delightful crunch and a burst of tangy passionfruit.

hasMenuItem.name: Skor Caramel Apple - Seasonal
hasMenuItem.description: Our famous caramel ice cream base, with house-made caramel that is hand folded with baked Granny Smith apples and Skor pieces sprinkled throughout.

hasMenuItem.name: Lemon Yogurt Cookie
hasMenuItem.description:
Our house-base is made from scratch with Greek yogurt and whole milk; it's lower in fat and sugar than usual. This refreshing ice cream has Italian lemon cookie curd throughout. 
Contains Gluten, Soy, Eggs, Peanuts, Dairy.

hasMenuItem.name: Strawberry
hasMenuItem.description:
Fresh whole strawberries are cooked down and infused in our house-made ice cream base. 
Contains Eggs.

hasMenuItem.name: Sprinkle Cake
hasMenuItem.description: 6" - serves 6-10 people. Fun layers of Vanilla, Cotton Candy and Bubble Gum ice cream on a Graham Cracker crust with your choice of either a Cotton Candy (pink) top layer or Bubble Gum (blue) top layer topped with sprinkles. Bubble gum flavour contains real bubble gum pieces.

review.reviewBody: Great cakes - quick service as well. Highly recommend
Instead of Lemon Yogurt Cookie , they served me Chocolate. They served the 4 dipped waffle Dipped Waffle Cones to me as 4 regular cones. disappointed.
Lemon Yogurt Cookie melted. Lemon Cookie Cheesecake is not fresh, Waffle Cone is missing. Not a good experience.
It was really good, it was a long way to my house but the icecream didn't melt so yayyyyyy
